\begin_inset Formula $\int d^{4}x\left[\mathcal{L}+J\phi+\frac{1}{2}i\varepsilon\phi^{2}\right]$
\end_inset

:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $\int d^{4}x\left[\mathcal{L}+J\phi\right]=\int d^{4}x\left[\frac{1}{2}\left(\partial_{\nu}\phi\right)\left(\partial^{\nu}\phi\right)-\frac{1}{2}m^{2}\phi^{2}+J\phi+\frac{1}{2}i\varepsilon\phi^{2}\right]=$
